require one transposition above the intended approximation ratio of $1.375$,
depending on how the input permutation is simplified. Then, we propose a new
$1.375$-approximation algorithm to solve TDP based on an algebraic formalism
which does not use simplification, ensuring the approximation ratio of $1.375$
